;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;">1</p></div><p style="margin-left: 15px;padding-bottom: 24px;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 20px;color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;font-weight: bold;"><strong style="letter-spacing: inherit;color: rgb(55, 80, 114);">自媒体创作者必选它！</strong></p></div><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">内容创作者真的很需要有网感的文字或者视频展现方式进行创作才能吸引到大家，这大概就是大家说的<span style="color: rgb(0, 128, 255);"><strong>流量密码</strong></span>吧！但是AI真的懂人类，了解什么是流量密码吗？行不行的上案例吧👇</p><p style="text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;padding: 0px 0.5em;margin-bottom: 24px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="327" data-backw="426" data-height="1070" data-imgfileid="100019363" data-ratio="0.7675925925925926" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1394" style="width: 418px;height: 321px;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: rgb(180, 180, 180) 0em 0em 0.5em 0px;font-size: 17px;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/5gR6KWHNb7TvynHBHPfavrx7FonqpU5Eq67yQkSs6Igu2lo60TC2e2U06jaoxrHrC1n116wTxPibS0t2ZfIXMug/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: justify;"></span></p><div style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div style="letter-spacing: inherit;"><p style="margin-bottom: -30px;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;">1</p></div><p style="margin-left: 15px;padding-bottom: 24px;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 20px;color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;font-weight: bold;"><strong style="letter-spacing: inherit;color: rgb(55, 80, 114);">小红书文案</strong></p></div><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">小红书种草文案，不如它俩王婆卖瓜，自卖自夸一下吧🫣。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">👉秘塔写作猫：<span style="color: rgb(0, 128, 255);"><strong>标明产品描述的要求</strong></span>，文案比较有真实性，种草感比较强，自带标签，不满意还可以一键多次生成；但是有时生成的内容与事实有偏差。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">另外，<span style="color: rgb(0, 128, 255);"><strong>秘塔写作猫</strong></span>对于各种使用场景还支持<span style="color: rgb(0, 128, 255);"><strong>批量生成</strong></span>（这里以小红书文案为例），而且生成的效果也不错，这个确实大大的提高了工作效率了！</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">👉蛙蛙写作：文案标题中自动添加符合的表情，与目标平台的风格相符，可以联网查询相关资料，降低出错率；但是文案内容有点官方，广告感较强，没太有种草感。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">这一局<span style="color: rgb(0, 128, 255);"><strong>秘塔写作猫胜出</strong></span>🏆</p><table><tbody><tr><td width="260" valign="middle" style="word-break: break-all;" align="center"><p style="padding: 0px 0.5em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="444" data-backw="239" data-height="3814" data-imgfileid="100019410" data-ratio="1.8583333333333334" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="2052" style=