-height: 1.75em;">👉蛙蛙写作：内容更注重画面感，每个场景都描述的很详细，支持选择视频中的角色人数，但是语言表达上广告感比较强，更适合企业官方宣传使用。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 128, 255);"><strong>还是秘塔写作猫</strong></span>🏆</p><table><tbody><tr><td width="260" valign="middle" style="word-break: break-all;" align="center"><p style="padding: 0px 0.5em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="574" data-backw="239" data-height="4976" data-imgfileid="100019408" data-ratio="2.401851851851852" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" data-width="2072" style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: rgb(180, 180, 180) 0em 0em 0.5em 0px;font-size: 17px;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5gR6KWHNb7TvynHBHPfavrx7FonqpU5EumycdUpNTxYricbfC2qpYcUg1AgfGmiahsu9PFicvKXiaOSPqs1uQuPsRQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p><span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: -webkit-center;text-wrap: wrap;">秘塔写作猫</span></p></td><td width="260" valign="middle" style="word-break: break-all;" align="center"><p style="padding: 0px 0.5em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="827" data-backw="239" data-height="3980" data-imgfileid="100019490" data-ratio="3.4611111111111112" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" data-width="1124" height="3890" style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: rgb(180, 180, 180) 0em 0em 0.5em 0px;font-size: 17px;" width="1124" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/TC6SuYvaia9sNIAxx0q65ZSeVeIOK22AJicwXaQnHR9R5XEuWYFdFfBrUqNw1hPUiccszMqic0984c4uGnHBMKZSPg/640?&amp;wx_fmt=png"></p><p style="word-break: break-all;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: -webkit-center;text-wrap: wrap;">蛙蛙写作</span><br></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p><br></p><div style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div style="letter-spacing: inherit;"><p style="margin-bottom: -30px;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;">1</p></div><p style="margin-left: 15px;padding-bottom: 24px;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 20px;color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;font-weight: bold;"><strong style="letter-spacing: inherit;color: rgb(55, 80, 114);">微信公众号文章</strong></p></div><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">👉秘塔写作猫：自动配图，文中的小标题也比较精炼，总体的内容格式也非常符合微信公众号的排版形式，文字表达比较流畅自然；但是，对于近期的热点事件，它生成的文案内容与事实不符，参考的资料有部分是虚假的，不能实时联网更新信息。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">👉蛙蛙写作：总体的内容虽然非常软文，但整体语言流畅，而且支持联网，并标注信息来源，内容也符合事实，不过小标题和配图需要自行添加。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 128, 255);"><strong>蛙蛙写作扳回一局🏆</strong></span></p><table><tbody><tr><td width="268" valign="top" style="word-break: break-all;"><p style="text-align: center;padding: 0px 0.5em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="1242" data-backw="247" data-croporisrc="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/TC6SuYvaia9sNIAxx0q65ZSeVeIOK22AJWzESJtCz4IyD262Szw5qK7OVpAHibIiawxG1n366P1yPv7gBWEIcDjjA/0?&amp;wx_fmt=png" data-cropx1="0" data-cropx2="1408" data-cropy1="22.801619433198383" data-cropy2="7102.704453441296" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100019488" data-ratio="5.027777777777778" data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style="width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: rgb(180, 180, 180) 0em 0em 0.5em 0px;font-size: 17px;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5gR6KWHNb7TvynHBHPfavrx7FonqpU5ECU3pmd99qnzHqPVEiceiaHiaaC56mIVKiboib5fWQx7XSbDs7icDFgIEa5pw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: -webkit-center;text-wrap: wrap;"></span><span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: -webkit-center;text-wrap: wrap;">秘塔写作猫</span></p><p><br></p></td><td width="268"