color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">总的来说秘塔写作猫在创作小红书文案、视频脚本、论文写作等方面的表现都优于蛙蛙写作，</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">但是蛙蛙写作🐸在微信公众号文章和公文写作也略胜于秘塔写作猫🐱。</p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: center;padding: 0px 0.5em;margin-bottom: 24px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="422" data-backw="561" data-croporisrc="https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5gR6KWHNb7TvynHBHPfavrx7FonqpU5ErO0sHaJAXPicmS6Jh8PC3WLIKIX0k1U6EDAvsmHTZjrol88Ezj7GhBg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" data-cropx1="0" data-cropx2="1151.946619217082" data-cropy1="0" data-cropy2="866.5266903914592" data-height="866" data-imgfileid="100019380" data-ratio="0.7527777777777778" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" data-width="1154" style="width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: rgb(180, 180, 180) 0em 0em 0.5em 0px;font-size: 17px;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5gR6KWHNb7TvynHBHPfavrx7FonqpU5EW24T2sDWk1eYwVNgcAArzLggibuMRTUxLgNgBwPhdWSpO8nVBMyzY7A/640?wx_fmt=jpeg"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">由于每个人的写作场景不同，所以适用的AI工具当然也有所不同，测评结果已经整理给大家啦，大家可以按需选择。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">欢迎大家关注我们，评论、转发这篇文章。或者加入我们的讨论社群与 AI 爱好者们交流。</p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;padding: 0px 0.5em;margin-bottom: 24px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="173" data-backw="562" data-height="180" data-imgfileid="100019384" data-ratio="0.3076923076923077" data-type="png" data-w="585" data-width="585" style="width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: rgb(180, 180, 180) 0em 0em 0.5em 0px;font-size: 17px;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/5gR6KWHNb7TvynHBHPfavrx7FonqpU5EcxrQwCD6JFpbDCgypTFWciaY0iaxnxq6q08AQEicUNquFiaHfLhnQgOF0A/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;padding: 0px 0.5em;margin-bottom: 24px;text-align: right;"><a target="_blank" href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyNjU2ODM2NQ==&amp;mid=2247564503&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=f2c7ca2c4f393f6f4e9254bc9120737f&amp;chksm=c236e615f5416f039e450005d6ac7fccaef5234b5f56d217c443cd23fa8ec4bea3a3ed2fddce&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect" textvalue="‍‍" linktype="text" imgurl="" imgdata="null" data-itemshowtype="0" tab="innerlink" data-linktype="1"><span class="js_jump_icon h5_image_link" style="width: 100%;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="139" data-backw="545" data-cropselx1="0" data-cropselx2="562" data-cropsely1="0" data-cropsely2="143" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100080880" data-ratio="0.2544444444444444" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="900" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jopKOlhibRBJ9aTJ8mW1kzHd1MBXiaiagFbXkJq6V2geKyhBHB6OIe9jgicUjfg8ecBTmicTzo0nKWJj84pibnUfP0CQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></span></a><a target=