        <title type="html"><![CDATA[华为“三界”齐亮相后，余承东卸任华为终端BG CEO]]></title>
        <id>2247564361_1</id>
        <link href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyNjU2ODM2NQ==&amp;mid=2247564361&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=fbcd40f16e5bcaaa0b3654dbc76abdad&amp;chksm=c236e68bf5416f9ddf50df9590229b981dc82239e7d3800a048c68ccd35af8ad55052fa2838e#rd"/>
        <updated>2024-05-01T02:13:11.000Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[<p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;" data-mpa-powered-by="yiban.io"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-backh="562" data-backw="562" data-imgfileid="100080709" data-ratio="1" data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/jopKOlhibRBIuvY4QQ30MHpwYicp4BZ2WWXpa2WLtxVz49zq2MTnU71icL1MSxGqUwTyLfVTBr1icrKcsXeCHe2tbw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"></p><div style="margin-bottom: 30px;padding-right: 8px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;text-align: start;background-image: none;background-position: initial;background-size: initial;background-repeat: initial;background-attachment: initial;background-origin: initial;background-clip: initial;"><p style="padding-top: 15px;letter-spacing: inherit;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);font-size: 13px;line-height: 21px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;">作者<span style="letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(221, 221, 221);">｜</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">唐健博</span><br style="letter-spacing: inherit;">邮箱<span style="letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(221, 221, 221);">｜</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">tangjianbo@pingwest.com</span></p></div><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;">智能手机时代，余承东几乎就是消费者心中华为手机的代言人。新能源汽车时代，余承东的身份又变成了华为智选车的代言人。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;">4 月 30 日，这种认知可能要发生变化了。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;">据 36 氪报道，华为内部发布人事调整文件，宣布余承东将卸任华为终端BG CEO 一职，仍保留终端BG 董事长职位。原华为终端BG、首席运营官何刚接任华为终端BG CEO。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;">截止发稿前，华为官方对此消息暂无置评，且华为公司官网的管理层信息仍保持原样。但可以看到，除了华为终端BG CEO 的身份之外，余承东同时还兼任智能汽车解决方案BU 董事长职位。</p><figure style="padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="361" data-backw="562" data-imgfileid="100080707" data-ratio="0.6426666666666667" data-type="png" data-w="750" height="1898" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 100%;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;height: auto;" title="" width="2954" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jopKOlhibRBIuvY4QQ30MHpwYicp4BZ2WWF0e8htqdz4phaGhb332uhj9uINKaR3lSFgJySOpu8xrzKic9xeynKNQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></figure><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;">在华为智能汽车解决方案BU 成立的五年时间里，余承东的身份发生了数次变化。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;">公开资料显示，华为于 2019 年 5 月正式成立智能汽车解决方案BU，与消费者BG 并列为一级部门，彼时由王军担任智能汽车解决方案BU 总裁。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;">2021 年 5 月，华为智能汽车解决方案BU 迎来人事调整，新增智能汽车解决方案BU CEO，由余承东出任，并同时兼任消费者BG CEO。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;">2023 年 9 月，余承东从智能汽车解决方案BU CEO 转任智能汽车BU 董事长。也正是在此人事调整之后，华为智选车业务开始走向正轨。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;">一直以来，华为都坚持不造车，帮助车企造好车。2021 年 12 月，华为与赛力斯共同推出“问界 AITO”品牌，第一台车为问界M5。但无论是第一代问界M5 还是问界M7，并没能将问界品牌打得响亮，问界一直位居新能源汽车二线阵列。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;">事情在 2023 年 9 月有了一些变化。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;">华为Mate 60 系列突然上线，同期发布的问界新M7 在全国名声大噪，加上合理的定价与智驾能力加持，问界新M7 瞬间成为新能源汽车行业的“野蛮人”，余承东称花了 5 个亿对问界新M7 进行升级改造，并在发布会上用了 5 个“遥遥领先”来形容问界新M7。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;">经此一役，问界品牌起死回生，跟上了新能源汽车的头部队伍。今年 3 月问界全系交付新车 31727 辆，环比增长 50%，连续三个位坐稳中国新势力品牌销量榜第一。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;">余承东个人似乎有一种魔力。外界对他有一个“余大嘴”称号，缘由来自于他行事高调，总爱在社交平台上说大话。但在采访中，余承东表示自己对此并不介意，因为吹过的牛都基本实现了。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;">余承东的底气来自于他过去在华为业务端所取得的成绩。官方资料显示，余承东于 1993 年正式加入华为，担任 3G 产品总监，历任无线产品行销副总裁、无线产品线总裁、欧洲片区总裁、华为终端BG CEO 等职位。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;">在余承东担任华为终端BG CEO 期间，低迷的华为手机业务一举成为“国民手机”，可以同苹果手机叫板。2019 年华为手机全球排名第二，中国市场第二，且在中高端市场中占比超过 50%。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;">在华为经受制裁之后，余承东的工作重心向华为智选车业务倾斜。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;">2023 年 11 月，华为鸿蒙智行联盟正式成立，并公布其业务下的第一款轿车，与奇瑞合作的智界 S7。华为鸿蒙智行成员总为四界，已公布的是问界、智界、享界，分别由华为与赛力斯、华为与奇瑞、华为与北汽共同打造的品牌。据传，最后一个华为与江淮合作的品牌，将会命名为“傲界”，将在 Q4 进行发布。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;">在余承东的带领下，华为智能汽车解决方案BU 几乎实现盈亏平衡。在此之前，余承东曾表示车BU 是华为唯一亏损的业务，并要在 2025 年实现盈利。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;">从目前的情况来看，余承东所吹的牛，可能又要提前实现。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;">4 月中旬，华为Pura 系列再次开启先锋计划，分批次开售，官网秒售罄。华为手机业务也逐渐开始反弹，从市场研究机构 Canalys 报告来看，2024 年第一季度，华为时隔 13 个季度，再度拿回中国市场份额第一。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;">在即将到来的 6 月，华为将举办华为开发者大会 HDC2024，自研系统 HarmonyOS NEXT 鸿蒙星河版将开启 Beta 测试。其系统将不再兼容安卓开源应用，仅支持鸿蒙内核和系统的应用。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;">余承东此次卸任终端BG CEO 之后，工作重心将会有什么变化，或许 6 月就会揭晓。</p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: center;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100080705" data-ratio="0.05555555555555555" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jopKOlhibRBIICkpD4bwucu7E3vVbBsQJ2ZN4cLvfH3jVhWmIhdXUdSYQ8Scf77QCGmGjmaSN5D4aHU4JqKnRSA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: right;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyNjU2ODM2NQ==&amp;mid=2247564294&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=e831c8f860d02dad329389778640c7f5&amp;chksm=c236e6c4f5416fd2bdec7d99c155e97f151cc5b7a34fae15fa2889754461cdfb90fc6bd16db9&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect" textvalue="‍‍" linktype="text" imgurl="" imgdata="null" data-itemshowtype="0" tab="innerlink" data-linktype="1"><span class="js_jump_icon h5_image_link" style="width: 100%;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="143" data-backw="562" data-cropselx1="0" data-cropselx2="562" data-cropsely1="0" data-cropsely2="143" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100080706" data-ratio="0.2544444444444444" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="900" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jopKOlhibRBK93Y1z1PKicD0APkibZznlEUt8shbe7RDh0l21cKtiaH2Om9M3DFuk40pcUiasejVCdW9WoPzrbDZ8zw/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></span></a><a target="_blank" href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyNjU2ODM2NQ==&amp;mid=2247564294&amp;idx=2&amp;sn=57592e97a6d29770a621998324d3fc25&amp;chksm=c236e6c4f5416fd2a3e6b1856fd285263feab2e442472c006cb17e1b69e09a1cef903e3e727c&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect" textvalue="‍‍" linktype="text" imgurl="" imgdata="null" data-itemshowtype="0" tab="innerlink" data-linktype="1"><span class="js_jump_icon h5_image_link" style="width: 100%;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="143" data-backw="562" data-cropselx1="0" data-cropselx2="562" data-cropsely1="0" data-cropsely2="143" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100080708" data-ratio="0.2544444444444444" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="900" style="outline: 0px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 100%;visibility: visible !important;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jopKOlhibRBK93Y1z1PKicD0APkibZznlEUqicuxh2o47iamVFCzrWEuicX7S4aPp4BTo3yMhdRic4ibsV3OuQMBzI7WfQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></span></a><a target="_blank" href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyNjU2ODM2NQ==&amp;mid=2247564194&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=46b06c0fa381a70ea71c1d3883ff05ab&amp;chksm=c236e160f5416876c2b3a4dea872950639b804ec78ffee7c819e5c362c553688311f37e39057&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect" textvalue="‍‍" linktype="text" imgurl="" imgdata="null" data-itemshowtype="0" tab="innerlink" data-linktype="1"><span class="js_jump_icon h5_image_link" style="width: 100%;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="143" data-backw="562" data-cropselx1="0" data-cropselx2="562" data-cropsely1="0" data-cropsely2="143" data-galleryid="" data-img