178, 178, 178);">（北京知春路地铁站出站口）</span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: justify;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;">而且，智谱在知春路这一站的广告和它在其他地方投放的并不完全一样。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;">这家同时做着toB和toC生意的公司，在Kimi的老窝用一种非常Kimi的风格投放着他们的广告。&nbsp; &nbsp;<o:page></o:page></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="295" data-backw="552" data-imgfileid="100080239" data-ratio="0.5339652448657188" data-type="png" data-w="633" height="295.0" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" width="552.010009765625" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jopKOlhibRBLjsT71yUC46kRe4dan1D3JWPkojPIv70FpU7klQkWoCDkW8Zn0uryTxREGz69VjDwicZ9uaQXv38A/640?wx_fmt=png"><span style="font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;">阿里云的员工们在全国的客户那儿推销完它们的大模型AI解决方案后，回到杭州，在机场会看到什么？</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;">答案是：字节旗下火山云的巨幅广告。</p><p style="text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="412" data-backw="552" data-imgfileid="100080235" data-ratio="0.7472353870458136" data-type="jpeg" data-w="633" height="413.010009765625" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" width="552.010009765625" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/jopKOlhibRBLjsT71yUC46kRe4dan1D3JqKmb7QpH4XXJIocjAuquv1FCr0RQOG3Gya6FnKiafG6TDpDqMJJnZpg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: center;">（杭州萧山机场T2航站楼）</span><span style="font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;text-align: justify;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;">在杭州萧山机场T2航站楼，在阿里云的地盘，火山表示要做你的下一朵云。<span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;">把自家的广告贴脸打到对手的腹地，这曾经是移动互联网最热闹时候最经常上演的戏码。而今天，大模型的火热让它以AI的名义再次上演。<span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><div style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div style="letter-spacing: inherit;"><p style="margin-bottom: -30px;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);letter-spacing: inherit;"></span><br></p></div></div><div style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div style="letter-spacing: inherit;"><p style="margin-bottom: -30px;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;">1</p></div><p style="margin-left: 15px;padding-bottom: 24px;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 20px;color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;font-weight: bold;"><strong style="letter-spacing: inherit;color: rgb(55, 80, 114);">智谱无处不在</strong></p></div><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;">为了看一看今天AI公司们的广告投放有多火热，我们在全国多个城市走了走，在关键的机场高铁站的点位，和人流量大的地铁站等关键位置，发现以AI为主题的广告已经蔓延开来。<span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;">对商务人士最能带来影响的机场高铁站，以toB的业务广告为主，在地铁等人流较大的区域则以toC为主。<span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;"></span></p><p style="text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="735" data-backw="552" data-imgfileid="100080238" data-ratio="1.3317535545023698" data-type="jpeg" data-w="633" height="736.010009765625" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" width="552.010009765625" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/jopKOlhibRBLjsT71yUC46kRe4dan1D3Jf0OkBic0V4AoV24Wia9csUichj1LIpxggXeT3ZepHq7AaF3KumYfdycGw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: center;">（图片来来源于现场实拍）</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;">而我们走了一圈的第一个感受是，智谱真的存在感超强。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;">在首都机场T3，你能看到它在展示自己的客户。<span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;">&nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="412" data-backw="552" data-imgfileid="100080237" data-ratio="0.7472353870458136" data-type="jpeg" data-w="633" height="413.010009765625" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" width="552.010009765625" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/jopKOlhibRBLjsT71yUC46kRe4dan1D3Jc39yfoD7Cibpay19HiaV8GAg3BZXaVpjpccPE2VKcNETeB28Bvk5TQeQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: center;">（北京首都机场T3航站楼）</span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: justify;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;">在一些商场，你能看到智谱洗脑一样的画面设计和台词：适合中国宝宝的大模型。<span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;"></span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="590" data-backw="552" data-imgfileid="100080243" data-ratio="1.0695102685624012" data-type="png" data-w="633" height="591.010009765625" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" width="552.010009765625" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jopKOlhibRBLjsT71yUC46kRe4dan1D3JLM43icutaLTDKevJmYiaxvkiaBZubkEMytpZm29wcud36xaZdhrMNic6LQ/640?wx_fmt=png"></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;">在地铁车厢里也能遇上。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="355" data-backw="552" data-imgfileid="100080240" data-ratio="0.6429699842022117" data-type="jpeg" data-w="633" height="355.010009765625" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" width="552.010009765625" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/jopKOlhibRBLjsT71yUC46kRe4dan1D3J1W4z2Yl7nRcL5BYw1lxkjlFzIfKgEsIDz0v7StF1k0D4TeKnLJYaLQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: center;">（图源北京地铁广告官方）</span><span style="font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;text-align: justify;"></span></p><p style="text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="492" data-backw="552" data-imgfileid="100080241" data-ratio="0.8909952606635071" data-type="jpeg" data-w="633" height="492.010009765625" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" width="552.010009765625" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/jopKOlhibRBLjsT71yUC46kRe4dan1D3Jp5egaZnxLIj1cOvqzgaThhFTqJAYSqgKbDG9bmRib4MMxaklfiajHvAg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: center;">（北京地铁1号线大望路站）</span></p><p style="text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="347" data-backw="552" data-imgfileid="100080242" data-ratio="0.6287519747235387" data-type="jpeg" data-w="633" height="347.010009765625" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" width="552.010009765625" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/jopKOlhibRBLjsT71yUC46kRe4dan1D3J4voq3x8ia68nYPOk83dej0eicFDlicE0DKVsMOxIFYr6T0DzOeYFN49Ug/640?wx_fmt=jpeg"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: center;">（北京地铁等待站内广告）</span><span style="font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;text-align: justify;"></span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;">而智谱这些地铁线下投放的位置，主要集中在海淀区中关村、五道口、知春路等科技企业密集的地方，以及像2号线/6号线换乘站朝阳门、1号线/10号线换乘站大望路这样的人群密集节点。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;">当然，智谱也没放过写字楼，海淀黄庄写字楼开发者更集中的地区，电梯间里一抬头便能看到智谱清言智能体的广告。</span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;"></span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="848" data-backw="552" data-imgfileid="100080244" data-ratio="1.5355450236966826" data-type="png" data-w="633" height="848.010009765625" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" width="552.010009765625" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jopKOlhibRBLjsT71yUC46kRe4dan1D3Jeh7k797xCZJPHE0pJcYpSsn9UEDLdjaKFLjibjqREibqJcflkJCovChg/640?wx_fmt=png"></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;">甚至在飞机上的小桌板背面，你也能看见智谱在提醒你用它写周报。&nbsp;</span> &nbsp;<o:page></o:page></p><p style="text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="735" data-backw="552" data-imgfileid="100080248" data-ratio="1.3317535545023698" data-type="png" data-w="633" height="736.010009765625" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" width="552.010009765625" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jopKOlhibRBLjsT71yUC46kRe4dan1D3J1lx6ptzBoqYVjT2qpdJlcutLpyXGT8Aeibibs7jo17CR20icOID42WR7A/640?wx_fmt=png"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot