        <title type="html"><![CDATA[rabbit r1第一批买家秀来了！经历轰动与质疑后，AI硬件销冠诞生]]></title>
        <id>2247563688_1</id>
        <link href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyNjU2ODM2NQ==&amp;mid=2247563688&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=620ae5550929b7d0ab5b919341d570df&amp;chksm=c236e36af5416a7cdd9366db02dae5568d8fb60799749e5815e8889711571e2a38ca6d4dc299#rd"/>
        <updated>2024-04-27T02:01:48.000Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[<p style="text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;" data-mpa-powered-by="yiban.io"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-backh="562" data-backw="562" data-cropselx1="0" data-cropselx2="562" data-cropsely1="0" data-cropsely2="419" data-imgfileid="100019914" data-ratio="1" data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style="width: 100%;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jopKOlhibRBLZBibcoxviab8J8eRuicyJuM00zicsgmocCa3HXFicMhDkVUW0FwIFMz2bicwR4K0gWqc1qBmag96WQx1g/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><div style="margin-bottom: 30px;padding-right: 8px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-image: none;background-position: initial;background-size: initial;background-repeat: initial;background-attachment: initial;background-origin: initial;background-clip: initial;"><p style="padding-top: 15px;letter-spacing: inherit;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);font-size: 13px;line-height: 21px;">作者<span style="letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(221, 221, 221);">｜</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">张潇雪</span><br style="letter-spacing: inherit;">邮箱<span style="letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(221, 221, 221);">｜</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">JessicaZhang@pingwest.com</span></p></div><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">1月9日，当rabbit inc.创始人吕骋站在摄像机前，首次向所有人举起手中那个四四方方的亮橙色迷你AI硬件时，他心里想的是：如果能卖出3千台就很高兴了。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">仅仅24小时后，首批1万台r1就被预订一空。再补货，再售罄…几个回合下来，到三个月后的今天，<span style="font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;">r1销量势如破竹冲破10万台。</span>在eBay等二手网站上价格甚至翻了10倍，最高被炒到了1999美元。</p><figure style="padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100019900" data-ratio="0.432" data-type="jpeg" data-w="750" height="1032" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 629px;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;height: auto !important;" title="eBay上挂出在纽约现场取货的r1，号称立等可邮" width="2390" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5gR6KWHNb7TggI8QfiaB2QJMPiaJiaxMflbkyUXUQ2QK89JROJiaaD1g6hrYca1EF3Vx0dBS7mZkmPSenHOwE0lB1A/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"><figcaption style="margin-top: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: center;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">eBay上挂出在纽约现场取货的r1，号称立等可邮</figcaption></figure><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">近期这些橙色的魔力小方块们陆续出厂发货，远渡重洋进入美国。本周二下午，团队在纽约TWA Hotel专门举办了一场「rabbit pickup party」，所有注册参加的买家们将成为首批把r1抱回家的幸运儿。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">吕骋也在现场做了全网第一个rabbit r1开箱，并隆重宣布素有「音频设备界苹果」之称的瑞典Teenage Engineering公司CEO兼创始人Jesper Kouthoofd将加入rabbit担任首席设计官。</p><figure style="padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100019899" data-ratio="0.556" data-type="png" data-w="750" height="1124" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 629px;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;height: auto !important;" title="" width="2022" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/5gR6KWHNb7TggI8QfiaB2QJMPiaJiaxMflbCqtA2ErS1qZz6giaVuyVd0uQN25mIlCx4wNeQwTGv1yd2GSPepN1BcQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></figure><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">观众和媒体记者簇拥在橙色布景的大厅。屏幕播放起r1一路经历的所有：从火爆CES、供不应求，到全网热议、各种关于“一个app就能解决”、“有手机为什么还要带它”的质疑声。后台的吕骋戴上耳麦向前走去，画外音问， Jesse，你会因为那些争议感到威胁吗？</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">“我不在乎。他们做他们想做的，我做我该做的。”</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">狂热的鼓掌和欢呼中，吕骋望着手里似乎还冒着热乎气的rabbit r1说：“这个颜色美得不真实。”</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">“网上曾有篇帖子说，之前我在keynote里提到的一半能实现就算不错了。现在看看我们在哪儿。今天我将向大家展示拿到全新r1的第一天，你们能做的每一件事。”</p><div style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div style="letter-spacing: inherit;"><p style="margin-bottom: -30px;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;">1</p></div><p style="margin-left: 15px;padding-bottom: 24px;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 20px;color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;font-weight: bold;"><strong style="letter-spacing: inherit;color: rgb(55, 80, 114);">r1开箱：从外观到上手的愉悦体验</strong></p></div><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">在包装盒外面，显示着「AI Companion」的产品描述，包装里有两个标志性的小兔子徽章饰品。</p><figure style="padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100019896" data-ratio="0.9146666666666666" data-type="jpeg" data-w="750" height="3749" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 629px;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;height: auto !important;" title="图源：YouTube@unboxtherapy" width="4096" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5gR6KWHNb7TggI8QfiaB2QJMPiaJiaxMflbKWJH3HQ1vMzp7QEXUSdfdBN0pxqibfia6KMTpE1TQ1ibcLLmJOBKfQEjg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"><figcaption style="margin-top: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: center;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">图源：YouTube@unboxtherapy</figcaption></figure><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">吕骋介绍，售价199美金无订阅费的r1除机器本身外，还附赠一款官配透明保护壳。方便外出携带，也可以立在桌面当支架。</p><figure style="padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100019898" data-ratio="0.7506666666666667" data-type="jpeg" data-w="750" height="3072" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 629px;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;height: auto !important;" title="图源：YouTube @ iJustine、X@raywongy" width="4096" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5gR6KWHNb7TggI8QfiaB2QJMPiaJiaxMflbwprHxjw4OZupv0znJjtU3us3fK4HxbgGCEre7xcPqu6HDnRVIoc9ag/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"><figcaption style="margin-top: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: center;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">图源：YouTube @ iJustine、X@raywongy</figcaption></figure><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">通体设计十分简约。一块2.88英寸触摸屏，侧边按键、滚轮、麦克风、摄像头，外加SIM卡插槽和USB-C充电接口。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">启动后选择使用移动数据或WIFI网络。根据提示扫码，连接自己的rabbithole账号激活设备，把需要的服务加进后台，再设置四位数付款码就可以使用了。</p><figure style="padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100019897" data-ratio="0.54" data-type="png" data-w="750" height="1304" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 629px;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;height: auto !important;" title="如果r1是个人助理，rabbithole就相当于它的大脑。这里也会实时同步用户与r1的每一次互动行为及生成的内容。" width="2412" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/5gR6KWHNb7TggI8QfiaB2QJMPiaJiaxMflbHXh9VubKjgJFyC3CqMmPA2yItqlmlSz2c6bbTef6iavQzyMDcZz7FHQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"><figcaption style="margin-top: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: center;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">如果r1是个人助理，rabbithole就相当于它的大脑。这里也会实时同步用户与r1的每一次互动行为及生成的内容。</figcaption></figure><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">团队重新优化了UI，让所有排列都和滚轮完美契合。知名YouTube红人@ iJustine上手后评价说“操作起来很丝滑，有无敌的满足感”。</p><figure style="padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100019904" data-ratio="0.5633333333333334" data-type="gif" data-w="600" height="338" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 629px;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;height: auto !important;" title="" width="600" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/5gR6KWHNb7TggI8QfiaB2QJMPiaJiaxMflbknHEI9mFfLiavjBumic9dicibuyVyFWicgLWzUD517IHnghXSxDkiaagPMqA/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></figure><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;">像这样摇两下就返回设置界面，调节亮度、音量、更改密码等。</span>还可以打开「enable terminal」，召唤一个不小于标准iPhone配备的键盘。此外也可以通过USB-C外接键盘，更多接口功能正在开发中。</p><figure style="padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100019905" data-ratio="0.5633333333333334" data-type="gif" data-w="600" height="338" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 629px;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;height: auto !important;" title="" width="600" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/5gR6KWHNb7TggI8QfiaB2QJMPiaJiaxMflbZzK5C17iamiakfCZKfickYKpsgzwibvJP42V4QQdfialzRXgktodl91EVcg/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></figure><div style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div style="letter-spacing: inherit;"><p style="margin-bottom: -30px;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;">1</p></div><p style="margin-left: 15px;padding-bottom: 24px;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 20px;color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;font-weight: bold;"><strong style="letter-spacing: inherit;color: rgb(55, 80, 114);">功能测评：试过后终于知道它为啥没直接做一个APP</strong></p></div><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">此次活动上吕骋一共演示了包括AI搜索、物体识别、图片生成、多语言翻译、语音笔记、录音总结、播放音乐、点餐和打车在内的9种功能。每次展示都引发现场叫好不断，还有人说单是「录音+总结要点」这一项就值回199刀票价了。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;">AI搜索：</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">尝试最简单的问天气，或更复杂一点的“2011年世界一级方程式锦标赛冠军车手、车队和设计师”，都是 2秒给出答案，反应慢的问题不存在了。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">r1还有一定的上下文记忆功能，可以回答连续提问，轻敲5次侧边键即可删除记忆。</p><figure style="padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100019902" data-ratio="0.5706666666666667" data-type="png" data-w="750" height="1140" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 629px;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;height: auto !important;" title="" width="1998" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/5gR6KWHNb7TggI8QfiaB2QJMPiaJiaxMflbUHiaopu4SUoSN4hPRyRUFwITMOkZ7JnyQoX7Wkot8b4z2DyOykyicxfQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></figure><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;">物体识别， 草图秒转csv表格：</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">r1自带一个360°可翻转相机当眼睛。不用拍照上传，双击侧边键打开「vision mode」就能告诉你眼前“看”到了什么。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">油管上近2400万粉丝的开箱博主@unboxtherapy测试用r1识别眼前的吉娃娃，结果精准。</p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><iframe class="video_iframe rich_pages" data-vidtype="2" data-mpvid="wxv_3431753201211490307" data-cover="http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FjopKOlhibRBLZBibcoxviab8J8eRuicyJuM0ZzORZIicOtulO7Wz0xqZ90wruy3kDB4AG3T0ydXaLahsv5Tg22HsZzw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" data-ratio="1.7777777777777777" data-w="1280" style="border-radius: 4px;" data-src="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_3431753201211490307"></iframe></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">还能阅读手机上密集排版的文章，如此细节识别能力。</p><figure style="padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Micro