data-src="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_3431757207862329350"></iframe></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">视频中他打开相机告诉r1，这是自己今天跟几个人各自讨论的话题和时间。要求转成csv表格，并在最右侧添加一列新的内容，分别填写与每个人接下来的to do list。仅过了3秒，Riley的邮箱就收到新消息提示。查看附件，两个字，完美。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">吕骋在活动上说，“尽管许多大模型都有视觉功能，但把一张纸上包含数字、单词的草图转换格式，粘贴附件再发邮件给你…目前r1是唯一能做到一整套动作的，它也是最便宜的！”——在场所有人表示狠狠爱了。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;">录音和总结</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">r1的录音功能可以帮助音乐工作者到大自然中采集声音、录制一小时以上重要工作会议，只需命令它‘start a recording session’即可。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">录制结束后，音频内容和一份文字总结立即自动同步到rabbithole后台，你可以下载全部无损wav格式音频及总结文本。</p><figure style="padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100019901" data-ratio="1" data-type="jpeg" data-w="750" height="1280" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 629px;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;height: auto !important;" title="" width="1280" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5gR6KWHNb7TggI8QfiaB2QJMPiaJiaxMflbBK3Q2CibVCXibXA3Ff10Cudnz2wrZmnwjAyibvTohGyyX5vcelcMqevmg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"></figure><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;">帮你叫车、点外卖：</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">只要在 rabbithole设置中连接了自己的Uber和Doordash账户，r1也能成为你的生活小助手。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">依然是按住侧边键提出叫车需求，报出出发地和目的地， r1就会自动去 Uber找到附近车辆。选择车型，并用开始设好的4位数密码付款后，它就会呼叫合适的司机来接你了。</p><figure style="padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100019909" data-ratio="0.5613333333333334" data-type="png" data-w="750" height="1070" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 629px;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;height: auto !important;" title="" width="1908" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/5gR6KWHNb7TggI8QfiaB2QJMPiaJiaxMflbWrkiahS5vgDcYibHwsFQxpxyBlibvKRytp2D46088hB9JZQOKynPtrhyg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></figure><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">点餐也同样简单， @ iJustine尝试了从附近HomeState餐厅点墨西哥卷饼的过程。需要注意的是博主的视频经过了编辑，实际上由于点餐应用有大量菜单图片需要加载，体验会比其它操作慢一点，但总体还是算流畅的。</p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><iframe class="video_iframe rich_pages" data-vidtype="2" data-mpvid="wxv_3431757851000127490" data-cover="http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FjopKOlhibRBLZBibcoxviab8J8eRuicyJuM04pXOsVpUAicAQ2jFiars83lvK9g5KPVHv24CTFMa0Da8yviayBT43Qibog%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" data-ratio="1.7777777777777777" data-w="1280" style="border-radius: 4px;" data-src="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_3431757851000127490"></iframe></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;">除了这些功能以外，r1还能做到：</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">随时随地将你的语音转为文本笔记，并存档在后台。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">在包括中文、英语、日语、泰语等57种语言之间进行双语翻译，是一个非常实用的便携式出境旅游搭子。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">使用Spotify流媒体播放想听的音乐。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">说出自然语言提示词，使用Midjourney生成图片内容。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">......</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;">整套体验下来，很多人惊喜地发现，r1真的不仅仅是一个“玩具”。</span>尽管以现在的AI技术和各类应用，人们可以分别用ABCD去完美驾驭这些任务，但当所有行为都集中到由一台小小的r1帮你完成呢？</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">我们此前已经知道， r1使用的是自己开发的rabbit OS专有操作系统。并集成了LLM（大语言模型）与LAM（大型动作模型），不仅能明白用户用自然语言说什么，还能通过对动作的不断学习和模仿，理解人的复杂意图，代表用户执行操作。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">“这只是LAM的第一个‘baby step‘。没人这么做过，所以即使演示很简单我们也不必感到羞耻。<span style="font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;">所有这些完全不是通过API或SDK，都是LAM直接帮你做的。</span>你不需要再打开无数应用跳转，r1就是你的agent。” 吕骋说。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">“我们要从零开始造一些东西。这些所有，就是我们没去做一个 APP的原因。”</p><div style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div style="letter-spacing: inherit;"><p style="margin-bottom: -30px;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;">1</p></div><p style="margin-left: 15px;padding-bottom: 24px;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 20px;color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;font-weight: bold;"><strong style="letter-spacing: inherit;color: rgb(55, 80, 114);">透露r1未来走向何方</strong></p></div><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">开箱演示过后，吕骋还向全场宣布了一些关于他们未来的振奋消息。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;">1. 首先是从r1推出至今的三个月里，公司又完成了一次全面升级。</span>团队从当初仅17人扩充到4倍技术人员规模，分别与11ElevenLabs、Perplexity、OpenAI、Anthropic达成合作伙伴关系，完成了由Sound Ventures领投的新一轮融资。</p><figure style="padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100019906" data-ratio="0.6013333333333334" data-type="png" data-w="750" height="1106" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 629px;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;height: auto !important;" title="" width="1838" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/5gR6KWHNb7TggI8QfiaB2QJMPiaJiaxMflbbQJR0hPC306dn1q4ibr5Rd0j7sa87LicLxQ4BYibgibDm6xLyIRHIouW0A/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></figure><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;">更激动人心的是，Teenage Engineering金字招牌、创始人和首席执行官Jesper Kouthoofd也被挖来rabbit兼任首席设计官。</span>二人已经合作了十几年，吕骋对接下来的并肩工作感到无比兴奋。</p><figure style="padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100019910" data-ratio="0.6666666666666666" data-type="jpeg" data-w="750" height="986" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 629px;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;height: auto !important;" title="图源：SYNTH History" width="1480" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5gR6KWHNb7TggI8QfiaB2QJMPiaJiaxMflbicsS1ib7EWZ3lSAK33vpNKvuHKuicBjqW1ldGuX27Q1ibtV0rhC3pJhaJg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"><figcaption style="margin-top: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: center;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">图源：SYNTH History</figcaption></figure><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;">2. 下一步将开发更多新功能。</span>例如闹钟、GPS、购物、更长的记忆能力、增添Spotify创立歌单，以及加入提示词作曲神器Suno等（下面满墙都可以期待）。</p><figure style="padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100019908" data-ratio="0.5493333333333333" data-type="png" data-w="750" height="1002" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 629px;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;height: auto !important;" title="" width="1822" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/5gR6KWHNb7TggI8QfiaB2QJMPiaJiaxMflbTuddRRrcszhyRHrl06dlcrIj02r0lFRLF9Shtibbgoic9bu7jwcDnXqA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></figure><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">rabbit也做了一些周边，帮用户把r1轻松携带到任何地方。</p><figure style="padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100019907" data-ratio="0.576" data-type="png" data-w="750" height="1078" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 629px;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;height: auto !important;" title="" width="1870" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/5gR6KWHNb7TggI8QfiaB2QJMPiaJiaxMflboJF3XrtjkpLGslfUPxSHFMbm2bC88jktKO1vHty33HiaHwh9Hz3h1mw/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></figure><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;">3. 关于teach mode（教学模式）的进展。</span>&nbsp;Rabbit的目标是今年内向公众推出teach mode，让大家可以“调教”自己的专属r1。但还是会采取先邀请少数人测试的方式分步推出，同时框定一些合规服务。“这个架构很新，我们没什么能借鉴的，所以慢慢来，给我们点信心。”</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;">4.预告下一代大型动作模型LAM 1.5。</span>关于这个吕骋没有透露太多，只是举例说未来当我们用手指向温度计，命令调节温度，LAM 1.5就可以执行。不是从digital interface学习，而是从真正的物理动作中学习。<span style="font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;">从幻灯片马赛克的「thing 1」来看，极有可能是一个手环的硬件外形</span>——有点玄幻，令人期待。</p><figure style="padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100019911" data-ratio="0.5546666666666666" data-type="png" data-w="750" height="976" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 629px;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;height: auto !important;" title="" width="1760" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/5gR6KWHNb7TggI8QfiaB2QJMPiaJiaxMflbf7toHx5iaGFCK3iasycHe5q7xKYicPgVK2UFA0HMNq3oMWia2S9DibU9GKA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></figure><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;">5. 一个完全适应用户的Generative UI 。</span>吕骋觉得计算机的未来趋势是个人定制化。在他愿景中，希望把rabbit OS升级为一个AI Native 桌面操作系统。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">整体来看，第一批到手的r1响应速度显著提升，除了点餐叫车，大部分请求都能在3秒内完成。并且操作方便友好，多种才艺傍身，还被用户发掘出许多惊喜的实用功能。</p><figure style="padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100019912" data-ratio="0.5626666666666666" data-type="png" data-w="750" height="1072" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 629px;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;height: auto !important;" title="人们在pick up party现场取走r1。" width="1906" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/5gR6KWHNb7TggI8QfiaB2QJMPiaJiaxMflb5NIuAFtRgPkGaU8rNlrBicic0ibwZb9BvmB4Knd7SL0JvntbKom5DMKfQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"><figcaption style="margin-top: 8px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: center;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">人们在pick up party现场取走r1。</figcaption></figure><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">吕骋和官推也第一时间在x上征集大家的第一批使用反馈，几乎每条必回。对于“连接移动数据时不能同步时间”、“登录需要密码的公共WIFI出现问题”、“需要更多灵活的提示词触发指令”等问题，他都表示：“我们正在解决，会尽快修复升级。”</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">“我们非常努力给大家带来r1，我们是一支很谦逊的团队，但绝不畏惧挑战。现在这个199美金的小东西有人类能体验到最棒最全的AI功能。虽然仍需很大改进，但我们会在这里解决问题，这一直是rabbit的目标。”</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">坐拥1800多万粉丝的油管数码一哥Marques Brownlee也拿到货了。就在10天前，他刚给Humane AI pin做了一期名为《我测过的最差产品》视频，一下子680万多播放量。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">网友们评论区看热闹说，r1是不是已经汗流浃背了？</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">“至少这绝对不是他review过最差的产品。”吕骋笑笑说。</p><figure style="padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100019913" data-ratio="1.1706666666666667" data-type="png" data-w="750" height="1374" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 629px;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;height: auto !important;" title="" width="1174" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/5gR6KWHNb7TggI8QfiaB2QJMPiaJiaxMflbtrUdGmhUo25D4iaJvKcsudqiae4ACr9pDnRnXsozN9DTDzchJKR7LJ0Q/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></figure><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;">（参考资料：https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W2pYTRdX5LA， https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LyXrziKPv9g&amp;t=22s，https://twitter.com/rileybrown_ai/status/1783178031927841011.封面图来自YouTube@unboxtherapy）</p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100080031" data-ratio="0.05555555555555555" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jopKOlhibRBIICkpD4bwucu7E3vVbBsQJ2ZN4cLvfH3jVhWmIhdXUdSYQ8Scf77QCGmGjmaSN5D4aHU4JqKnRSA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: right;"><a target="_blank" href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyNjU2ODM2NQ==&amp;mid=2247563661&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=924655ecbc8beff1a79562d501dea39a&amp;chksm=c236e34ff5416a594ce890703a30188ebd2ed91d1ad3b75bd716cac38214a6af9a732d76ec1a&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect" textvalue="‍‍" linktype="text" imgurl="" imgdata="null" data-itemshowtype="0" tab="innerlink" data-linktype="1"><span class="js_jump_icon h5_image_link" style="width: 100%;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="143" data-backw="562" data-cropselx1="0" data-cropselx2="562" data-cropsely1="0" data-cropsely2="143" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100080034" data-ratio="0.2544444444444444" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="900" style="width: 100%;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png