    <entry>
        <title type="html"><![CDATA[直播技术“破圈”：赛事直播不止于比赛]]></title>
        <id>2247563661_1</id>
        <link href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyNjU2ODM2NQ==&amp;mid=2247563661&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=924655ecbc8beff1a79562d501dea39a&amp;chksm=c236e34ff5416a594ce890703a30188ebd2ed91d1ad3b75bd716cac38214a6af9a732d76ec1a#rd"/>
        <updated>2024-04-26T02:00:03.000Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[<p style="text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;" data-mpa-powered-by="yiban.io"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="562" data-backw="562" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100079893" data-ratio="1" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jopKOlhibRBJ2yGgEibxzhfWu9JiaWJDK17tbXichicAbGWia4DPELRtG3kdZJhT7IaPf8CicmDRr9K4JdEF2wU4ia3Bfg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><div style="margin-bottom: 30px;padding-right: 8px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-image: none;background-position: initial;background-size: initial;background-repeat: initial;background-attachment: initial;background-origin: initial;background-clip: initial;"><p style="padding-top: 15px;letter-spacing: inherit;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);font-size: 13px;line-height: 21px;">作者<span style="letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(221, 221, 221);">｜</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">Yoky</span><br style="letter-spacing: inherit;">邮箱<span style="letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(221, 221, 221);">｜</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">yokyliu@pingwest.com</span></p></div><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">1998年世界杯，罗纳尔多在决赛中迷失方向，法国队在本土夺冠，中国的球迷们只能通过次日的新闻和重播，来回味那场足球盛宴。在那个电视还是奢侈品的年代，国际赛事对于中国观众来说，是一段段远渡重洋的录像带，是一份份报纸上的文字直播，是深夜里收音机中传来的激动人心的解说。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">随着直播技术的诞生与普及，国际赛事——如世界杯和NBA正在逐渐成为中国观众日常生活中不可或缺的一部分。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;">大型体育赛事不仅代表着体育竞技的巅峰，更是媒体技术进步的展示窗口。在这个时代，直播技术已成为衡量一个国家媒体发展水平的重要标准。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">如今，观看大型赛事不再局限于单向的观看，而是变得更加互动和多元。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">享受“一起看比赛”的同步体验；聆听大V解说，深入理解赛事背后的战术与故事；甚至</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">体验“明星陪看”的陪伴感。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">时代轮回，又到了考验直播技术的时候。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">4月2</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">5</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">日，声网发布了全新的赛事直播方案，支持毫秒级的低延迟全球分发，结合多路径、动态路由策略，为</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">直播平台</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">提供超低延迟、</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">高清</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">画质</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">的</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">直播</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">技术</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">服务。这不仅保障了赛事直播的流畅性和清晰度，更通过云上解说、</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">低码高清</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">等创新</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">技术</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">，降低了</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">平台</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">成本，提高了</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">观众</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">体验</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><div style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div style="letter-spacing: inherit;"><p style="margin-bottom: -30px;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;">1</p></div><p style="margin-left: 15px;padding-bottom: 24px;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 20px;color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;font-weight: bold;"><strong style="letter-spacing: inherit;color: rgb(55, 80, 114);">信号传输，走进“黄金时代”</strong></p></div><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">在那个电视机还是稀罕物的年代，每逢奥运会，一</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">村</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">一台的电视机便成了全村的焦点，男女老少围坐在一起，目不转睛地盯着屏幕，共同见证着中国女排的辉煌。然而，正当女排姑娘们扣下决定性的一球时，屏幕上却突然出现了“信号中断”的字样，那一刻的沮丧和遗憾，至今仍然让许多老一辈体育迷记忆犹新。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;">时间流转至今天，直播技术已经发生了翻天覆地的变化。更快、更高、更强，这三大需求，已经成为衡量直播技术是否达标的基本标尺。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">举几个肉眼可见的例子。比如音画不同步的问题，想象一下，当你正紧张地盯着屏幕，期待着球员的临门一脚时，</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">解说</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">声音却提前了半拍，那种错位感足以让你的观赛体验大打折扣。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">视频流的画面清晰度也是观众关注的焦点。在高速运动的体育赛事中，任何一个模糊的瞬间都可能让你错过关键的细节</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">据声网直播技术负责人何胜名介绍,声网赛事直播解决方案基于 NTP 可以保证解说嘉宾各端对齐,直播画面差严格小于3帧,解说音轨与赛事画面同步。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">声网也基于PTS技术，解决了画面平滑切换等问题。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">声网直播</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">产品</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">负责人</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">李志杰</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">介绍道：声网的PTS对齐技术可以保证在绝大多数时候，</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">观众</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">对于</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">画面的切换都是平滑发生，帧连续的，不会出现掉帧、漏帧的情况。</span></p><figure style="padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100079883" data-ratio="0.3626666666666667" data-type="png" data-w="750" height="458" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 629px;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;" title="" width="1265" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jopKOlhibRBJ2yGgEibxzhfWu9JiaWJDK17bhH1eJoW8476Wk6HG3Uc14tv63SKWcrROKXmSlfR4CbIkjHm1dG47A/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></figure><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">为了应对不同网络环境下的挑战，声网还采用了自适应码率传输（ABR）技术，能够根据</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">观众</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">网络状况动态调整传输码率，优化网络资源的使用，</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">有效缓解观众的网络波动带来的突发问题</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;">同时，</span><span style="font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;">直播画面</span><span style="font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;">的清晰度也是观众关注的焦点。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">比如运动员的表情、足球划过球网的瞬间等等。因此，如何提供高清、流畅的视频流，是直播平台必须面对的挑战。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;">但这中间存在一个技术上的悖论，画质本身和不卡顿是有冲突的，码率越高清晰度越高，而码率越高则对用户的网络要求越高，卡顿率也就越高。想要同时保证低码和高清，需要在技术上实现极大的创新。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">声网</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">通过低码高清技术</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">，对视频源进行高效压缩。通过优化编码算法，声网能够在不牺牲画质的前提下，大幅度降低视频的码率需求。这种技术尤其在处理高速运动画面时表现出色，它能够有效捕捉到运动员的细微表情和动作，同时减少因高码率带来的网络传输负担。</span></p><figure style="padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100079881" data-ratio="0.4493333333333333" data-type="png" data-w="750" height="568" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 629px;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;" title="" width="1265" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jopKOlhibRBJ2yGgEibxzhfWu9JiaWJDK17xdrNUY9JXicaAMH7LeUo5y5HDibyNxYbGvlY2zVsabwFJBMs6IXDeJVQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></figure><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">其次，</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">声网赛事直播解决方案</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">支持广播级</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">&nbsp;4K&nbsp;</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">端到端稳定传输</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">,</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">且全面支持华为</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">&nbsp;HDR Vivid,</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">提供静态</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">HDR&nbsp;</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">和动态</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">&nbsp;HDR&nbsp;</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">的全端渲染。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">此外，加入了声网自研的低码高清</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">”</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">技术及</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">&nbsp;ABR&nbsp;</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">方案，在提升画质的同时能大幅降低码率</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><figure style="padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100079884" data-ratio="0.45866666666666667" data-type="png" data-w="750" height="846" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 629px;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;" title="" width="1846" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jopKOlhibRBJ2yGgEibxzhfWu9JiaWJDK1760E5jdc4HAD1lZAFOHvlHHldaFjXVpLP3ZCEicgzyEJLA2NUdxr64MQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></figure><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">声网还采用了深度学习算法对视频内容进行分析，通过识别视频中的关键信息和高频信号，算法能够在编码过程中对这些区域进行优化处理。例如，在体育赛事直播中，算法会优先保证运动员和球的运动轨迹等关键信息的清晰度，而对于背景等相对静态的部分则采取较低的编码质量，从而在整体上平衡了画质和码率。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;">而比这些技术问题更让平台头疼的，是安全问题。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">随着网络技术的发展，视频内容被盗链的风险也在不断增加。一旦内容被盗链，不仅平台的权益受到侵害，观众的观赛体验也会受到影响。因此，如何保证视频内容的安全，避免被盗链，成了直播平台必须面对的难题。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">“</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">有平台</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">在使用传统的CDN服务直播世界杯比赛时，由于缺乏有效的安全保护措施，被恶意第三方非法盗链直播内容。结果，在短短一天时间内，</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">流失了约2T的带宽，造成了高达</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">百万元</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">的经济损失</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">，</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">欲哭无泪啊。”李志杰讲道。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">正是在这种背景下，</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">声网</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">以其军工级的信号加密技术，实现RTC（实时通信）通道的全程加密，确保从主播到观众的整个传输过程中，信号内容都得到严格保护。声网的加密技术不仅涵盖了传输层的加密，还包括了内容层面的加密，这意味着即便信号被非法截获，没有相应的解密密钥也无法还原出原始内容。</span></p><figure style="padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100079882" data-ratio="0.5346666666666666" data-type="png" data-w="750" height="1022" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 629px;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;" title="" width="1910" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jopKOlhibRBJ2yGgEibxzhfWu9JiaWJDK1744PClzib9mCgRfpBib1LjCOjzDKyMVCRohJcUKyhpL29mrrokUD3UoQg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></figure><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">简单的说，</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">低延迟传输通道实现了端到端的双重加密，即传输过程加密和内容加密，为直播内容的安全加上了双重锁。这种加密方式有效防止了类似上述案例中的盗链事件，保障了直播平台的带宽资源和经济利益不受侵害。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><div style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div style="letter-spacing: inherit;"><p style="margin-bottom: -30px;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;">1</p></div><p style="margin-left: 15px;padding-bottom: 24px;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 20px;color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;font-weight: bold;"><strong style="letter-spacing: inherit;color: rgb(55, 80, 114);">直播技术的阅兵与练兵</strong></p></div><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">随着直播技术的不断进步，用户的观看习惯也在悄然发生变化。他们不再满足于单向的观看体验，而是渴望更加个性化和互动性强的直播方式。声网正是洞察到这一趋势，通过技术创新，不断探索直播的新场景，满足用户的多元化需求。</span></p><figure style="padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: inherit;text-align: start;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100079885" data-ratio="0.384" data-type="png" data-w="750" height="486" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;width: 629px;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;" title="" width="1265" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jopKOlhibRBJ2yGgEibxzhfWu9JiaWJDK17QgokJywibP1qmMYDGnbiaNQqXicgVNA4jgriafibLYhaqoSbIYlZU8m4lGg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></figure><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">比如邀请</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">好友同时在线观看赛事直播</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">，</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">共庆进球得分精彩瞬间。在享受超低延时的比赛直播的同时，</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">还</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">可以随时与好友语音或视频实时聊天</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">或是</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">让明星以视频互动直播的形式与观众共同观看赛事</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">、</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">综艺</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">类</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">节目，为观众提供 “追更+追星” 的互动陪伴式体验</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;">这不仅是技术上的创新，更是对用户需求的深刻理解。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">上述提到的这些场景</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">，</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">都需要极低延时的传输作为保障，</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">背后都是基于声网的SD-RTN™</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">，它通过软件技术优化了全球范围内的传输路径，以实现低延迟、高可靠性的音视频数据传输。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">SD-RTN™的核心优势在于其智能化的路由选择和故障恢复能力。通过实时监控网络状态，SD-RTN™能够自动选择最佳的传输路径，避开拥堵和不稳定的网络区域，从而减少数据传输的延迟。此外，它还能够在网络出现故障时迅速切换到备用路径，保证通信的连续性和稳定性。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">据李志杰介绍，</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">声网已经开始和各大平台进行合作，从这届欧洲杯开始，用户就可以</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">在部分平台的房间，享受全网最快的直播观看</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">体验。它可以保证在500ms内将画面传输到观众眼中，相比传统的</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">HLS</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">、</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">FLV</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">通道最高降低</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">90%</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">，观众端直播画面首帧出图</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">时间</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">&lt;400ms</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">，做到精彩赛事随点随开。观众端音视频丢包边界</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">80%</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">，极端弱网也能保障流畅。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;">更重要的是，基于SD-RTN™的跨区域传输能力，能够为直播平台提供</span><span style="font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;">显著的成本节约优势。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">传统的直播往往依赖于昂贵的专线服务来保证数据传输的稳定性和实时性，这不仅限制了直播的灵活性，也带来了高昂的费用。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">这意味着直播平台可以使用成本更低的互联网线路，而非昂贵的专线服务，从而显著降低了传输成本。而云端解说功能省去了租赁线下场地的费用，同时也减少了因场地限制而带来的各种潜在成本。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">在</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">现实应用</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">场景上，SD-RTN™广泛应用于多种实时互动场景，包括在线教育、远程医疗、社交直播等。例如，在国际赛事直播中，SD-RTN™能够确保全球观众无论身处何地，都能享受到低延迟、无卡顿的观赛体验。在远程办公场景中，它支持多人视频会议的稳定运行，即便在网络条件不佳的情况下也能保持流畅的沟通。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;">这说明这项技术的成功应用，预示着直播技术将渗透到更广泛的领域，带来更深远的影响。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">比如在电竞领域，从早期的《魔兽争霸》到如今的《英雄联盟》，游戏直播的普及曾受限于传播力和带宽等因素，SD-RTN™的低延迟和高并发处理能力，也能够帮助电竞直播能够触及更广泛的观众群体。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">对于直播平台而言，技术的创新带来了新的互动模式。传统的直播模式下，手机发烫、画质不清晰、成本高昂等问题一直困扰着直播行业。而云直播方案的推出，通过降低对硬件的依赖，不仅解决了这些问题，还为直播设备的选择提供了更多的可能性。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">在未来，直播技术将面临更加复杂和多变的挑战。它不仅需要满足用户对于高清、流畅、实时的观看需求，还要能够适应不断涌现的新场景和新应用。从电竞直播到在线教育，从远程医疗到社交互动，直播技术的触角正在不断延伸，其影响力也在逐渐扩大。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-right: 8px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-left: 8px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: inherit;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(48, 48, 48);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;">“更高、更快、更强”，不止是体育竞技精神，更是直播技术更长远的征程。</span><span style="letter-spacing: inherit;"></span></p><p style="text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="187" data-backw="562" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100075262" data-ratio="0.3333333333333333" data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-w="900" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/jopKOlhibRBJkgJKzaoAxCyoficlRCRSbQzamZPYiaLg10DFflQbSa7S9LicXckrcwgX9GjQVEm0S6ykBshRdWEJpg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="446" data-backw="562" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100079015" data-ratio="0.7933333333333333" data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-w="900" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/jopKOlhibRBIj6uryK1h7GU61GdaDr0UeicFic3QaGqM1QEaqIRziaCgFqV6xnc6aBWauhFKtHBuFflEkM83N38gsA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100079889" data-ratio="0.05555555555555555" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="1080" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jopKOlhibRBIICkpD4bwucu7E3vVbBsQJ2ZN4cLvfH3jVhWmIhdXUdSYQ8Scf77QCGmGjmaSN5D4aHU4JqKnRSA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style